==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Serbo-Croatian]] [[papar]] (ground peper) or '''paprika''' (peper, the vegetable) via Hungarian.

===Noun===
'''paprika'''

#A [[mild]] [[sweet]] [[cultivar]] of the [[pepper]] family ''[[Capsicum anuum]]''
#the dried [[spice]] of the vegetable used in [[Hungarian]] cooking.
#(''colour'') a bright reddish orange colour, like that of the dried paprika.
